records.name: Hilton Maldives Amingiri Resort & Spa

descriptions.direction: Located in Amingiri, Hilton Maldives Amingiri Resort & Spa is on a private beach. Male Fish Market and Chaandhanee Magu are worth checking out if shopping is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Rasfannu and Angsana Beach. Looking to get your feet wet? Fishing and swimming adventures can be found near the property.
descriptions.general: Nestled amidst the tranquil blue waters of North Malé Atoll, Hilton Maldives Amingiri Resort & Spa offers beachfront accommodation. Easily accessible via a 20-minute premium speedboat transfer from Velana International Airport it offers various facilities, such as restaurants, an outdoor swimming pool and a bar. This 5-star resort offers a private beach area and a kids' club. The accommodation provides a 24-hour front desk, room service and currency exchange for guests.
descriptions.other: The resort is accessible by a 20-minute speedboat ride from Velana International Airport. A shared premium speedboat transfer is arranged for all our guests according to their international flight schedule (arrival/departure time) and is available 24/7. Third-party transport arrangements are not permitted.
